<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Appointment Reminder</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333333;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #007bff;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #777777;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .button.whatsapp {
            background-color: #25D366;
        }

        .details {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .details strong {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 100px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            Appointment Reminder
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello John Doe,</h2>
            <p>This is a reminder for your upcoming appointment.</p>
            <div class="details">
                <p><strong>Title:</strong> Health Check-Up</p>
                <p><strong>Date:</strong> June 15, 2024</p>
                <p><strong>Time:</strong> 10:00 AM</p>
                <p><strong>Duration:</strong> 1 Hour</p>
                <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Annual Health Examination</p>
                <p><strong>Location:</strong> 123 Health St, Wellness City</p>
                <p><strong>Consultant:</strong> Dr. Smith</p>
            </div>
            <p>Please be prepared and arrive on time.</p>
            <a href="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/render?action=TEMPLATE&text=Health+Check-Up&dates=20240615T100000Z/20240615T110000Z&details=Annual+Health+Examination&location=123+Health+St,+Wellness+City"
                class="button">Add to Calendar</a>
            <button class="button" onclick="sendSMS()">Send SMS Reminder</button>
            <a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=0249434803&text=Reminder%3A%20Health%20Check-Up%20on%20June%2015%2C%202024%20at%2010%3A00%20AM.%20Location%3A%20123%20Health%20St%2C%20Wellness%20City.%20Consultant%3A%20Dr.%20Smith."
                class="button whatsapp">Share on WhatsApp</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2024 Wellness Clinic. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>

